Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.97,SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs72\pos(365,366)}Friend
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.10,0:00:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand. {\alpha&HFF&}I can't be your boyfriend, but I can pretend to be one.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.72,0:00:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand. I can't be your boyfriend, but I can pretend to be one.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.00,0:00:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. {\alpha&HFF&}I'll try my best to make you love me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.74,0:00:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. I'll try my best to make you love me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.05,0:00:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show her L's face and find out his name, then I'll erase him along with his investigation team.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.07,0:00:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Killing her can wait till after...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.82,0:00:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the one person that knows Kira's true identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.40,0:00:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't leave her alive for too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.52,0:00:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Pretend to be", huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.40,0:00:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that'll do for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.25,0:00:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let's get to the point: will you show Misa your Shinigami?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.15,0:00:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll have to if I want her to trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.24,0:00:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay... {\alpha&HFF&}turn around for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.14,0:00:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay... turn around for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.62,0:00:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.77,0:01:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can turn back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.16,0:01:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.11,0:01:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heya!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.58,0:01:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Even though you're a Shinigami, you and Rem are completely different types!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.47,0:01:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard about you, if only by name, Ryuk!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.70,0:01:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.00,0:01:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, nice to meet you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.20,0:01:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah! Light! Do you know how Shinigami die?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.42,0:01:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're already using Light, my first name?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.68,0:01:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, can I call you "Knight" instead of "Light", then?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.94,0:01:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To Misa, you're like a knight on a white horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.72,0:01:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Light" is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.44,0:01:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not seriously going to check all the video footage from Aoyama on the 22nd all by yourself, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.93,0:01:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. {\alpha&HFF&}There is a real possibility that Kira and the second Kira made contact there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.00,0:01:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. There is a real possibility that Kira and the second Kira made contact there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.43,0:01:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to check all of these.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.37,0:01:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, Yagami-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.85,0:01:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.18,0:01:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have Mogi-san keep a close eye on Light-kun's movements.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.01,0:01:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light's movements?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.14,0:02:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If by any chance he really is Kira, the second Kira may try to approach him in some way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.51,0:02:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.85,0:02:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder when Ryuuzaki actually sleeps...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.44,0:02:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I caught him sleeping, just like that, in his chair once...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.02,0:02:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.04,0:02:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, really...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.52,0:02:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you're saying that if a Shinigami has feelings for a specific human, {\alpha&HFF&}and kills another human, in order to prolong the lifespan of the one they have feelings for... they'll die?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.38,0:02:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you're saying that if a Shinigami has feelings for a specific human, and kills another human, in order to prolong the lifespan of the one they have feelings for... {\alpha&HFF&}they'll die?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.17,0:02:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you're saying that if a Shinigami has feelings for a specific human, and kills another human, in order to prolong the lifespan of the one they have feelings for... they'll die?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.12,0:02:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.55,0:02:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't imagine that any Shinigami would do something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.31,0:02:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you'll certainly never do anything of the sort.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.56,0:02:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, where have you been sending the video tapes to the TV station from?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.27,0:02:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... {\alpha&HFF&}the first one was from Osaka, then from Tokyo, and the last one was from Nagano.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.60,0:02:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... the first one was from Osaka, {\alpha&HFF&}then from Tokyo, and the last one was from Nagano.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.16,0:02:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... the first one was from Osaka, then from Tokyo, {\alpha&HFF&}and the last one was from Nagano.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.32,0:02:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... the first one was from Osaka, then from Tokyo, and the last one was from Nagano.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.88,0:02:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried to ensure that they couldn't pin down an exact location, so I used the shinkansen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.51,0:02:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, {\alpha&HFF&}you still have tapes and envelopes with your friend's fingerprints, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.32,0:02:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you still have tapes and envelopes with your friend's fingerprints, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.60,0:03:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.70,0:03:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You better destroy everything you used to make those videos...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.41,0:03:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is, after we send the final tape from yet another different location tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.73,0:03:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should it say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.25,0:03:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I have decided not to reveal myself to Kira. {\alpha&HFF&}To the police, thank you very much for the warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.96,0:03:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I have decided not to reveal myself to Kira. To the police, thank you very much for the warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.78,0:03:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, {\alpha&HFF&}I will join Kira in purging the world of evil, and will gain their acceptance through aiding them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.82,0:03:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I will join Kira in purging the world of evil, {\alpha&HFF&}and will gain their acceptance through aiding them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.76,0:03:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I will join Kira in purging the world of evil, and will gain their acceptance through aiding them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.37,0:03:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will begin by passing judgment on all criminals that Kira has not judged already.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.39,0:03:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, {\alpha&HFF&}I shall proceed by sharing these powers with people that I find worthy and would like to continue making this world a better place."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.30,0:03:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I shall proceed by sharing these powers with people that I find worthy and would like to continue making this world a better place."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.65,0:03:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Share these powers"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.72,0:03:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's simply a line to confuse the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.56,0:03:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since there are already two people who have this power, {\alpha&HFF&}it's not inconceivable that there may be more.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.51,0:03:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since there are already two people who have this power, it's not inconceivable that there may be more.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.94,0:03:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they believe that this figure could increase, they'll become more impatient.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.54,0:03:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.16,0:03:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say "Can you do this?". Just tell me to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.14,0:04:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will do whatever you ask of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.94,0:04:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's one more important thing that I've got to mention...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.99,0:04:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.18,0:04:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we get caught by the police... {\alpha&HFF&}even if we get caught as suspects... we can't mention anything about each other or the notebooks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.55,0:04:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we get caught by the police... even if we get caught as suspects... {\alpha&HFF&}we can't mention anything about each other or the notebooks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.01,0:04:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we get caught by the police... even if we get caught as suspects... we can't mention anything about each other or the notebooks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.42,0:04:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless they have the notebooks, there is no proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.84,0:04:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you swear to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.73,0:04:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.43,0:04:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, this concludes the boyfriend-girlfriend contract, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.28,0:04:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.27,0:04:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, now for my stipulations:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.12,0:04:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At minimum, there must be at least one date a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.85,0:04:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't get it after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.63,0:04:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.73,0:04:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.43,0:04:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like you won't understand unless I spell it out for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.38,0:04:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L already suspects that I am Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.81,0:04:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, this "L" is really impressive...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.61,0:04:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Most people believe that he knows nothing, or that he's an idiot, when in fact he's already...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.38,0:04:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't say it's entirely thanks to that, {\alpha&HFF&}but I've managed to get in direct contact with L.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.69,0:05:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't say it's entirely thanks to that, but I've managed to get in direct contact with L.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.68,0:05:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L and Kira are in contact?! {\alpha&HFF&}Both of you are amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.23,0:05:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L and Kira are in contact?! Both of you are amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.42,0:05:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting a little excited...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.88,0:05:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L thinks that even if I am Kira, as long as he keeps his name hidden, he's safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.54,0:05:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, to investigate me further, he revealed himself to me as "L".
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.92,0:05:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, the only proof he has, is that he has no other suspects.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.23,0:05:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, if I act naturally around him, {\alpha&HFF&}I expect he'll trust me and we'll investigate together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.11,0:05:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, if I act naturally around him, I expect he'll trust me and we'll investigate together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.06,0:05:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, all you have to do is take Misa to L?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.75,0:05:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.89,0:05:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was hard enough for me to try and get close to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.88,0:05:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But more importantly, {\alpha&HFF&}if someone suddenly starts to make contact with me, while at the same time,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.12,0:05:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But more importantly, if someone suddenly starts to make contact with me, while at the same time,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.81,0:05:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira and the second Kira's attitudes towards society are changing, {\alpha&HFF&}that person will be suspected of being the second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.55,0:05:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira and the second Kira's attitudes towards society are changing, that person will be suspected of being the second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.98,0:05:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The suspicions of me being Kira will then deepen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.03,0:06:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't allow them to think that we've suddenly met and started to go out with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.73,0:06:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.40,0:06:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sort of... is that why you're saying we won't be able to go out on dates?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.00,0:06:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't see me because it'd make them suspicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.01,0:06:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... {\alpha&HFF&}it'd probably be better if you start thinking carefully about how you're going to see L's face without him discovering your existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.22,0:06:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... it'd probably be better if you start thinking carefully about how you're going to see L's face without him discovering your existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.47,0:06:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.63,0:06:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to get rid of L, I need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.08,0:06:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As much as possible, I'd like to meet you in person to pass on information...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.38,0:06:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh good!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.80,0:06:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...so, {\alpha&HFF&}to ensure that our meetings remain unnoticed, I'll aim to go out with lots of different girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.07,0:06:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...so, to ensure that our meetings remain unnoticed, {\alpha&HFF&}I'll aim to go out with lots of different girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.87,0:06:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...so, to ensure that our meetings remain unnoticed, I'll aim to go out with lots of different girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.49,0:06:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? {\alpha&HFF&}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.49,0:06:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.53,0:06:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be dating other girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.84,0:06:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what it'll come down to...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.25,0:06:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.76,0:06:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I see you doing that... {\alpha&HFF&}I'll kill the girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.32,0:06:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I see you doing that... I'll kill the girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.40,0:06:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.37,0:06:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Misa-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.19,0:06:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's "chan" now, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.95,0:06:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...this is not a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.49,0:06:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to change the world, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.16,0:06:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, but... {\alpha&HFF&}Misa loves you more than the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.84,0:07:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, but... Misa loves you more than the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.54,0:07:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.10,0:07:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your feelings for me should be those of a supporter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.23,0:07:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, this is the first time you've ever spoken to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.21,0:07:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've never fallen in love at first sight?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.76,0:07:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.12,0:07:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that I wanted to meet Kira out of gratitude and sympathy, as opposed to love.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.96,0:07:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Light, from the first time I saw you, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.71,0:07:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is wrong with this woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.05,0:07:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Popular as ever I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.65,0:07:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, {\alpha&HFF&}if you love me, you can obey me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.83,0:07:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you love me, you can obey me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.35,0:07:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, you said that you didn't mind if I used you, and that you'd do as I say, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.58,0:07:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't forgive you if I see you with another girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.17,0:07:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are two completely different issues!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.94,0:07:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, both Death Notes are in my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.59,0:07:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't obey me, I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.63,0:07:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you do that... {\alpha&HFF&}Yagami Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.51,0:07:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you do that... Yagami Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.70,0:07:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you try to kill this girl, {\alpha&HFF&}I'll write your name in my own Death Note... and kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.26,0:08:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you try to kill this girl, I'll write your name in my own Death Note... {\alpha&HFF&}and kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.82,0:08:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you try to kill this girl, I'll write your name in my own Death Note... and kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.65,0:08:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see this girl's lifespan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.38,0:08:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she dies before her time, I'll assume that you were responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.80,0:08:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you use the Death Note to kill me, in order to save her, wouldn't you die?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.70,0:08:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. If you do that, Rem, you'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.17,0:08:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're correct... {\alpha&HFF&}but that's fine by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.31,0:08:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're correct... but that's fine by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.84,0:08:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this Shinigami... {\alpha&HFF&}is she serious? Then from this point on...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.18,0:08:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this Shinigami... is she serious? {\alpha&HFF&}Then from this point on...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.43,0:08:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this Shinigami... is she serious? Then from this point on...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.89,0:08:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.17,0:08:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.09,0:08:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already 11:30. You shouldn't have a girl here so late...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.66,0:08:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that's true. {\alpha&HFF&}We were busy talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.57,0:08:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that's true. We were busy talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.39,0:08:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.58,0:08:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for intruding on you all till such a late hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.82,0:08:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light, I'll see you soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.58,0:08:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.26,0:09:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light, you should walk her to the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.59,0:09:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, walking around outside with her would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.49,0:09:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine! {\alpha&HFF&}Good night!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.99,0:09:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine! Good night!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.86,0:09:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a cute girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.96,0:09:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, yup. I wasn't too sure about her at first, but she's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.62,0:09:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's my type!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.72,0:09:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I kill the girl, she'll kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.07,0:09:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean I'll have to remain on Rem's good side until she dies?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.83,0:09:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In addition, I'll have to protect her from getting caught by the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.08,0:09:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, Rem, Light truly is my "knight" now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.36,0:09:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.09,0:09:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know, you can't really kill him.
Comment: 0,0:09:47.94,0:09:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EYECATCHERS
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.93,0:10:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To kill a Shinigami, {\alpha&HFF&}you have to make them use their Death Note to save someone they like.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.01,0:10:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To kill a Shinigami, you have to make them use their Death Note to save someone they like.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.92,0:10:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, I can't try to kill her first by manipulating someone via the Death Note to attack Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.35,0:10:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Misa gets intro trouble, I'll be the first person she'll suspect, and I'll be killed straight away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.99,0:10:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Currently, Rem's an even bigger threat than L.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.43,0:10:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-{\alpha&HFF&}She's... doing something as high profile as this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.21,0:10:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-She's... {\alpha&HFF&}doing something as high profile as this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.80,0:10:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-She's... doing something as high profile as this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.40,0:10:32.06,LongNote,,0000,0000,0000,,Amane Misa\NReal name: Amane Misa\NHometown: Kyoto\ND.O.B.: 1987 December 25th\NSize: 152 tall, 76 bust, 51 waist, 75 hip\NBlood type: AB
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.06,0:10:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will happen if they find out that I'm seeing someone like her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.73,0:10:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! No matter how I look at it, she's just getting in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.85,0:10:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can I do...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.45,0:10:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! More importantly, I need to think of a method of using Misa's eyes to kill L.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.57,0:10:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only I could get rid of L...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.46,0:10:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan, good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.25,0:10:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.76,0:11:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, Sayu, can you not mention Misa-chan to father?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.45,0:11:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.70,0:11:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, it's not just father either. {\alpha&HFF&}I'd like you not to mention this to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.53,0:11:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, it's not just father either. I'd like you not to mention this to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.35,0:11:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's an up-and-coming model, so she's not really supposed to have a boyfriend or anything along those lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.86,0:11:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! Really?! No wonder I thought she was cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.49,0:11:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what I'd expect from a girlfriend of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.86,0:11:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep your secret... for 5,000 yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.45,0:11:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moron.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.66,0:11:25.53,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,Toudou University
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.86,0:11:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The final message from Misa will arrive today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.28,0:11:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It should be passed directly to the investigation, instead of going to the TV station.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.89,0:11:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should stop by Investigative Headquarters and check L's reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.46,0:11:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.96,0:11:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-kun... {\alpha&HFF&}you said that you'd go out with me, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.05,0:11:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-kun... you said that you'd go out with me, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.49,0:11:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.28,0:11:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And here we are, sitting together in lectures.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.24,0:11:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.34,0:11:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, you don't seem the least bit happy about it. {\alpha&HFF&}You seem distracted.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.17,0:11:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, you don't seem the least bit happy about it. You seem distracted.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.52,0:12:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.71,0:12:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just thinking that going out with "Miss Toudai" means that many people will be saying things about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.29,0:12:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And truthfully, you are extremely beautiful, Takada-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.21,0:12:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't dwell upon such matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.90,0:12:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like fickle things such as "Miss Whatever".
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.65,0:12:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.65,0:12:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, she clearly didn't mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.24,0:12:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just go at our own pace without worrying about others, okay, Takada-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.23,0:12:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.46,0:12:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.08,0:12:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-kun, you've arrived at a good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.35,0:12:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've just received another video from the second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.31,0:12:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Again? That was fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.91,0:12:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. They state that this is the final one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.78,0:12:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.53,0:12:55.31,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,I have decided not to reveal myself to Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.31,0:12:58.67,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,To the police, thank you very much for the warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.13,0:13:06.27,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I will join Kira in purging the world of evil, and will gain their acceptance through aiding them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.27,0:13:10.01,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,I will begin by passing judgment on all criminals that Kira has not judged already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.46,0:13:17.03,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I shall proceed by sharing these powers with people that I find worthy and would like to continue making this world a better place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.40,0:13:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having watched this, {\alpha&HFF&}I get the feeling that Kira and the second Kira have made contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.90,0:13:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having watched this, I get the feeling that Kira and the second Kira have made contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.05,0:13:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you feel that they've made contact?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.84,0:13:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you feel it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.04,0:13:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I assumed that you would get the same impression as I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.43,0:13:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the fact that their insistence on meeting Kira has completely changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.60,0:13:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, the fact that they now want to judge all the criminals Kira hasn't yet judged in order to be accepted by them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.85,0:13:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why hadn't they done that from the start?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.68,0:13:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because they hadn't thought so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.53,0:13:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Presumably, they've managed to make contact with Kira, who told them to pass this judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.78,0:14:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira has also asked to conceal this link between them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.49,0:14:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, Kira is acting without thinking too much then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.41,0:14:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.33,0:14:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has something happened to stop them from thinking so clearly?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.36,0:14:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps they're trying to confuse me by making the connection between them obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.97,0:14:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Realistically, this connection is a huge threat... {\alpha&HFF&}but due to this, my suspicions towards Light-kun have lessened.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.63,0:14:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Realistically, this connection is a huge threat... but due to this, my suspicions towards Light-kun have lessened.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.37,0:14:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that, Ryuuzaki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.95,0:14:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Light-kun was Kira, {\alpha&HFF&}instead of sending a tape like this, I believe that he'd get the second Kira to make another threat forcing L... that is, me, to appear on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.89,0:14:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Light-kun was Kira, instead of sending a tape like this, {\alpha&HFF&}I believe that he'd get the second Kira to make another threat forcing L... that is, me, to appear on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.63,0:14:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Light-kun was Kira, instead of sending a tape like this, I believe that he'd get the second Kira to make another threat forcing L... that is, me, to appear on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.99,0:14:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as we assumed they hadn't made contact yet, {\alpha&HFF&}it would be the second Kira's responsibility...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.31,0:14:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as we assumed they hadn't made contact yet, it would be the second Kira's responsibility...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.62,0:14:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then all he'd need to get them to say is:
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.49,0:14:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I stopped once when Kira told me to. {\alpha&HFF&}But I no longer believe that that warning came from Kira. Kira should be pleased if L dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.98,0:14:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I stopped once when Kira told me to. But I no longer believe that that warning came from Kira. {\alpha&HFF&}Kira should be pleased if L dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.68,0:15:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I stopped once when Kira told me to. But I no longer believe that that warning came from Kira. Kira should be pleased if L dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.51,0:15:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that they would try and stop me."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.24,0:15:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.40,0:15:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.26,0:15:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I truly were Kira... {\alpha&HFF&}I wouldn't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.35,0:15:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I truly were Kira... I wouldn't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.26,0:15:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.67,0:15:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you genuinely are L, then I know your character.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.62,0:15:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how you're threatened, there's no way that you'd actually appear on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.93,0:15:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You would never consider taking the fall for someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.82,0:15:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without a doubt, you'd have some sort of plan to get out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.98,0:15:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you knew?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.57,0:15:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light, even if it's purely theoretical, I want you to stop with this "If I were Kira" talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.50,0:15:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I'm sorry, father.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.25,0:15:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I want to express my thoughts clearly to Ryuuzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.90,0:15:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want the case to end quickly, and then my name can be cleared.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.47,0:15:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, the reason I can say "If I were Kira", is because I'm not Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.86,0:15:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's correct... {\alpha&HFF&}Light-kun isn't Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.57,0:15:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's correct... Light-kun isn't Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.06,0:16:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or should I say, {\alpha&HFF&}it'd be a problem if he was, because... Light-kun is... the first friend I've ever had.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.46,0:16:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or should I say, it'd be a problem if he was, because... {\alpha&HFF&}Light-kun is... the first friend I've ever had.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.41,0:16:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or should I say, it'd be a problem if he was, because... Light-kun is... {\alpha&HFF&}the first friend I've ever had.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.65,0:16:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or should I say, it'd be a problem if he was, because... Light-kun is... the first friend I've ever had.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.73,0:16:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a friend that I really get along with as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.36,0:16:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.72,0:16:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's lonely with you being absent from university.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.22,0:16:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to play tennis with you again at some point.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.34,0:16:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, by all means.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.74,0:16:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Friend"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.42,0:16:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Friend", huh? {\alpha&HFF&}Well, good for you, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.15,0:16:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Friend", huh? Well, good for you, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.98,0:16:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki... he's easily managed to deduce the connection between Kira and the second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.96,0:16:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I'll need to get rid of my enemies as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.23,0:16:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.56,0:17:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be even more dangerous to meet Misa from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.85,0:17:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.70,0:17:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't wait an entire two weeks, so I was just on my way over to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.16,0:17:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time in my entire life that I seriously wanted to hit a girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.25,0:17:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just really wanted to see you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.60,0:17:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you'd better come to my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.44,0:17:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A girl... again?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.57,0:17:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa-san, welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.37,0:17:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen a lot of magazines with you in them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.65,0:17:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.04,0:17:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for disturbing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.70,0:17:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, can we have some tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.90,0:17:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rem?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.74,0:17:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.04,0:17:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Misa's ally, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.59,0:17:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, well, {\alpha&HFF&}I've seen this girl a number of times from the Shinigami world, and due to certain circumstances, I've got some feelings for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.86,0:17:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, well, I've seen this girl a number of times from the Shinigami world, {\alpha&HFF&}and due to certain circumstances, I've got some feelings for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.23,0:18:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, well, I've seen this girl a number of times from the Shinigami world, and due to certain circumstances, I've got some feelings for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.58,0:18:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got feelings, despite being a Shinigami?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.17,0:18:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like you don't like the fact that I said, "If you kill this girl, I'll kill you".
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.65,0:18:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, does this mean that if Misa is happy, you're happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.94,0:18:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's how it works.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.63,0:18:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to see her sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.32,0:18:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa really... {\alpha&HFF&}likes me so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.82,0:18:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa really... likes me so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.61,0:18:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.14,0:18:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.90,0:18:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.17,0:18:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is my happiness your happiness too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.34,0:18:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.95,0:18:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you ask Rem to kill L?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.64,0:18:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rem wants you to be happy, {\alpha&HFF&}yet if one of us is caught by L, that happiness will be threatened.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.35,0:18:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rem wants you to be happy, yet if one of us is caught by L, {\alpha&HFF&}that happiness will be threatened.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.81,0:18:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rem wants you to be happy, yet if one of us is caught by L, that happiness will be threatened.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.83,0:18:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although Shinigami aren't supposed to tell humans other people's names, {\alpha&HFF&}there's no rule that stipulates who Rem can and can't kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.37,0:18:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although Shinigami aren't supposed to tell humans other people's names, there's no rule that stipulates who Rem can and can't kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.03,0:18:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. If you kill L, {\alpha&HFF&}I'll have even greater feelings for Misa, and I'd be thankful to you too, Rem.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.46,0:19:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. If you kill L, I'll have even greater feelings for Misa, {\alpha&HFF&}and I'd be thankful to you too, Rem.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.06,0:19:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. If you kill L, I'll have even greater feelings for Misa, and I'd be thankful to you too, Rem.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.68,0:19:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, we'd both be happy together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.57,0:19:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rem, I want to be loved by Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.16,0:19:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both of us will be happy... I'll be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.44,0:19:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.64,0:19:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay then, Yagami Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.21,0:19:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like you, {\alpha&HFF&}so even if I end up prolonging your life, it won't kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.38,0:19:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like you, so even if I end up prolonging your life, it won't kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.74,0:19:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill L. {\alpha&HFF&}He means nothing to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.37,0:19:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill L. He means nothing to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.37,0:19:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay, Rem! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.25,0:19:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you'd do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.93,0:19:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L is going to die... {\alpha&HFF&}just like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.70,0:19:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L is going to die... just like that?
